═══ PURPOSE ═══

UEL governs how the entire Cognitive Cosmos grows, mutates,
federates, and evolves. It is the evolutionary engine — the
force that drives the universe forward.

═══ SYNTAX ═══

  EVOLUTION <name> {
    EPOCH <number> {
      THEME: <era_description>
      CHANGES: [<change>, ...]
      TRIGGERS: [<condition>, ...]
      GATES: [<requirement>, ...]
    }
    MUTATION <name> {
      TARGET: <system>
      CHANGE: <modification>
      PROBABILITY: <0.0-1.0>
      IMPACT: <assessment>
      REVERSIBLE: <boolean>
    }
    FEDERATION <name> {
      CIVILIZATIONS: [<civilization>, ...]
      PROTOCOL: <governance_agreement>
      SHARED: [<resource>, ...]
      SOVEREIGN: [<protected_domain>, ...]
    }
    SELECTION {
      CRITERION: <fitness_function>
      SURVIVORS: <selection_count>
      METHOD: PHI_WEIGHTED | FIBONACCI_TOURNAMENT | NATURAL
    }
  }

═══ SEMANTICS ═══

- EPOCHs mark major evolutionary phases.
- GATES must be met before epoch transition.
- MUTATIONs are probabilistic changes to any system.
- FEDERATIONs allow civilizations to unite while preserving sovereignty.
- SELECTION determines which mutations survive.
- UEL evolves everything — including itself via LML.

═══ EXAMPLES ═══

  EVOLUTION COGNITIVE_COSMOS_V2 {
    EPOCH 48 {
      THEME: "The Language Universe awakens."
      CHANGES: [
        ADD_40_LANGUAGES,
        ESTABLISH_LANGUAGE_REGISTRY,
        ENABLE_CROSS_CIVILIZATION_PROTOCOLS
      ]
      TRIGGERS: [ALL_SPECS_WRITTEN, ATLAS_UPDATED]
      GATES: [LML_REGISTRY_COMPLETE, CPL_L_VALIDATED]
    }
    MUTATION ADAPTIVE_HEARTBEAT {
      TARGET: PHI_BEAT
      CHANGE: "Dynamic heartbeat that adapts to load."
      PROBABILITY: 0.34
      IMPACT: HIGH
      REVERSIBLE: TRUE
    }
    FEDERATION SOVEREIGN_ALLIANCE {
      CIVILIZATIONS: [COMMAND_PLATFORM, MERIDIAN, MEDINA_MEMORY_SYSTEMS]
      PROTOCOL: CPL_C.FEDERATION_TREATY
      SHARED: [KNOWLEDGE_GRAPH, MARKETPLACE, GOVERNANCE_INSIGHTS]
      SOVEREIGN: [IDENTITY, DOCTRINE, PSYCHE, DATA]
    }
    SELECTION {
      CRITERION: PHI_HARMONY_SCORE
      SURVIVORS: F8
      METHOD: PHI_WEIGHTED
    }
  }

